sub_title: Operations & Supply Chain Manager (South Europe) en Pool System
summary:
Ey, thanks for visiting! Let me tell you a bit of me and what drives me. I'm multi disciplinary and enthusiast person; with background on Commercial, Sales and Innovation, I'm a Logistic and operational guy, with focus on reverse logistics and depot operations. More than 9 years experienced through supply chain and process optimization and managing integration projects between operations and IT.

I'm always looking for new challenges and thinking out of the box.
